OL,11,Fmillion in 2022-23 and #0.9 million in
OL,12,F2018-19.
OL,14,FThe report also found that this
OL,15,Fexpenditure is disproportionate to the
OL,16,Fnumber of households placed in such
OL,17,Faccommodation.
