OL,6,FIt was found that around #4.5 million
OL,7,F(6%) of the 2023/24 spend by the
OL,8,FHousing Executive was directed at
OL,9,Fpreventing homelessness, despite this
OL,10,Fbeing at the heart of its Homelessness
OL,11,FStrategy.
OL,13,FMeanwhile a lack of suitable,
OL,14,Fpermanent social housing was found to
OL,15,Fbe impacting the Housing Executive's
OL,16,Fability to tackle homelessness
OL,17,Feffectively.
