OL,4,C'squeezing homelessness services'
OL,6,FMany of these households rely on
OL,7,Ftemporary accommodation while they
OL,8,Fwait for a permanent home.
OL,10,FMs Carville described an
OL,11,F"unprecedented demand" for
OL,12,Fhomelessness services, in particular
OL,13,Ftemporary accommodation.
OL,15,FShe said this has been impacted by an
OL,16,Finadequate supply of social housing,
OL,17,Fthe impact of the coronavirus pandemic
OL,18,Fand the cost-of-living crisis.
