OL,4,C'squeezing homelessness services'
OL,6,F"Homelessness has impacts across
OL,7,Fsociety, with long-term consequences
OL,8,Ffor health and education outcomes, and
OL,9,Fthe costs to the public purse are
OL,10,Fsignificant and rising," Ms Carville
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"Dealing with these issues is complex
OL,14,Fand my report acknowledges the efforts
OL,15,Fbeing made by the Housing Executive
OL,16,Fand those working in the sector under
OL,17,Fchallenging circumstances.
