OL,4,C'squeezing homelessness services'
OL,6,F"However, in order to ensure the best
OL,7,Fuse of public money, there is a need
OL,8,Fto reduce spending on hotels and B&Bs,
OL,9,Fand for an increased focus on
OL,10,Fhomelessness prevention and the supply
OL,11,Fof new social housing.
OL,13,F"Until these key issues are resolved,
OL,14,Fdemand for homelessness services is
OL,15,Flikely to continue to escalate to a
OL,16,Fpoint where it may become financially
OL,17,Funsustainable."
